Terms and conditions:
1)Functions use are not allowed
2)Loop
3)Conditional statement
4)Array
5)variable declare

2)Loop With Semicolon



Loop:

1)for :

for(initization;condition;incre/decre)
{

}

2)while:Entry control loop

initialization

while(condition)
{
	statement 
}

3)do while:Exit Control Loop

initialization
do
{
	statement ;	
}
while(condition);


